e":"Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"select":"channel","channelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"#content","cachedResultName":"#content"},"text":"=🚨 {{ $json.workflow }} failed at {{ $json.failedNode }}: {{ $json.errorMessage }}","otherOptions":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.slack","typeVersion":2.3,"position":[7438,1420],"id":"8694a97c-3272-4de2-a49d-9a415b80b8c0","name":"Escalate Failure to Slack","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"resource":"databasePage","operation":"create","databaseId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Draft Database"},"title":"={{ $json.topic || $json.draftId }}","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.notion","typeVersion":2.2,"position":[7762,1420],"id":"d11f45a9-8a6f-4167-b2ac-b6a48aa645f5","name":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"content":"### Weekly Schedule\n\nStarts the workflow on a timer — weekly. No input data; downstream nodes fetch what they need.\n\nNext: Keep Valid Drafts","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"46573745-7dfa-3886-b657-18c30b58ee28","name":"Note: Weekly Schedule"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Keep Valid Drafts\n\nDrops items that fail the condition; only qualifying items continue (no false branch).\n\nNext: Frame the Assignment","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"ba92ea9e-f048-d395-dedd-29d444d283e2","name":"Note: Keep Valid Drafts"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Frame the Assignment\n\nShapes the item: writes `assignment`, `deadline`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Coordinator Agent","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"375cdb2e-591a-4124-6169-19ff2007d489","name":"Note: Frame the Assignment"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Coordinator Agent\n\nThe AI brain: reads the input, decides which attached tools to call (and in what order), then composes the answer.\n\nPorts: ①→ Unpack Sections · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n⚠ failures exit via the error rail","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"23b198bf-20f1-922a-3eb5-bde3595e1464","name":"Note: Coordinator Agent"},{"parameters":{"content":"### OpenAI Chat Model\n\nChat model powering the AI step (model: `gpt-4o-mini`). Swap providers here without rewiring.\n\nFeeds **Coordinator Agent** as `languageModel`\n\n🔑 OpenAI API key","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[885,1090],"id":"9fae42b6-2ca7-f88a-53ee-d6f2e08189b9","name":"Note: OpenAI Chat Model"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Research Specialist (Sub-workflow)\n\nSpecialist sub-workflow exposed as a callable tool — one narrow capability per tool.\n\nFeeds **Coordinator Agent** as `tool`","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[804,1510],"id":"2bbc9f30-3101-77a3-7e84-6ff53c6d4831","name":"Note: Research Specialist (Sub-workflow)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Draft Specialist (Sub-workflow)\n\nSpecialist sub-workflow exposed as a callable tool — one narrow capability per tool.\n\nFeeds **Coordinator Agent** as `tool`","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1060,1750],"id":"e53f2d3f-e212-bcbd-6af5-d77b0fd2683a","name":"Note: Draft Specialist (Sub-workflow)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Enforce Result Schema\n\nForces the agent's answer into the JSON schema below — downstream nodes rely on this exact shape.\n\nFeeds **Coordinator Agent** as `outputParser`","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1222,1090],"id":"4166c391-9932-e630-7c31-b7a0f632fdc9","name":"Note: Enforce Result Schema"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Unpack Sections\n\nExplodes the `output.sections` array into one item per element.\n\nNext: Persist Deliverable to Notion","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1546,520],"id":"9a1a7d76-2e13-a4a0-9bbf-6e5a6179d480","name":"Note: Unpack Sections"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Persist Deliverable to Notion\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Fingerprint for Idempotency · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1870,520],"id":"0ca47b55-cfff-e227-73cb-4e757db41488","name":"Note: Persist Deliverable to Notion"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fingerprint for Idempotency\n\nCustom JavaScript: Build a stable idempotency key per draft (djb2 hash, no deps)\n\nNext: Drop Already-Processed Items","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2194,520],"id":"2fa4d1a5-b5e5-a535-aa15-cee30d53aa38","name":"Note: Fingerprint for Idempotency"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Drop Already-Processed Items\n\nCross-execution dedupe: remembers keys it has processed before and drops repeats — the idempotency guard.\n\nNext: Serialize Run Output (CSV)","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2518,520],"id":"dcbe12f2-092f-137c-fa22-8ffab2be7082","name":"Note: Drop Already-Processed Items"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Serialize Run Output (CSV)\n\nSerializes items to a CSV binary file.\n\nNext: Archive Row Snapshot","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2842,520],"id":"a6d46275-bebb-6c8b-c415-873db5194e63","name":"Note: Serialize Run Output (CSV)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Row Snapshot\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3166,520],"id":"28a23238-0c0b-0fe7-7704-8f6b5152ad18","name":"Note: Archive Row Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow\n\nDelegates to a reusable sub-workflow (single-responsibility building block) and waits for its result.\n\nPorts: ①→ Record Sub-workflow Result · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3490,520],"id":"a6953bcd-646e-219c-c535-c98286a2bc76","name":"Note: Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Record Sub-workflow Result\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Enrich with Reference Data","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3814,520],"id":"93a378c1-8950-8aad-3672-59178755557e","name":"Note: Record Sub-workflow Result"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Enrich with Reference Data\n\nGET https://enrichment.example.com/v2/lookup — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Fold In Enrichment Fields · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4138,520],"id":"a9a9d67c-92e2-fad9-52cd-5bab9dbbf335","name":"Note: Enrich with Reference Data"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fold In Enrichment Fields\n\nShapes the item: writes `enrichedAt`, `enrichmentSource`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Stamp Completion Time","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4462,520],"id":"3a331ad4-86f2-3012-e457-3844a90ebe32","name":"Note: Fold In Enrichment Fields"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Completion Time\n\nStamps `completedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Persist Run Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4786,520],"id":"95da46fe-a5a2-bbd3-4b3b-7737fda0edad","name":"Note: Stamp Completion Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Persist Run Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Load Previous Snapshot","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5110,520],"id":"52eb3590-a7e4-d0c2-027b-f06618198476","name":"Note: Persist Run Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Load Previous Snapshot\n\nnotion — `getAll` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Compute Drift vs Snapshot · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5434,520],"id":"b35b8ad0-ae17-b50b-fce4-78c3f9ff1995","name":"Note: Load Previous Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Compute Drift vs Snapshot\n\nCustom JavaScript: Compare current metrics with the previous snapshot\n\nNext: Cap Batch Volume","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5758,520],"id":"92dfd0a3-f7eb-945f-f517-e69e326c0067","name":"Note: Compute Drift vs Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Cap Batch Volume\n\nCaps the stream at 100 items to protect downstream quotas.\n\nNext: Sort Drafts Newest First","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6082,520],"id":"93a8db65-74e8-ac89-aa76-53fdbd0739fd","name":"Note: Cap Batch Volume"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Sort Drafts Newest First\n\nOrders items (newest first) so limits and digests pick the most relevant records.\n\nNext: Tag Pipeline Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6406,520],"id":"b567f3f8-266d-e731-88aa-0c1645aebd05","name":"Note: Sort Drafts Newest First"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Tag Pipeline Metadata\n\nShapes the item: writes `pipeline`, `version`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6730,520],"id":"e9c9c106-aa2b-f27a-2306-c83a1f153a42","name":"Note: Tag Pipeline Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7054,520],"id":"a2b6d0b7-0abb-3d26-d6fd-8d7a0b83116c","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7378,520],"id":"33fc16a3-7802-ede0-fe27-05193f026465","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7702,520],"id":"600fc51c-f734-241b-c2da-64c9f646ddfb","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7054,1540],"id":"f4125df6-e1e7-a99c-e99d-3a534b9b28fc","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7378,1540],"id":"28649a38-d46a-670f-e45c-52d916516abc","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7702,1540],"id":"4675def7-f7e2-dc1e-c760-c0d745f16595","name":"Note: Park in Dead-Letter Queue"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Generate social posts with Google Sheets and WordPress hands-free\n\n**Pattern:** Content Generation · **Level:** Architect · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nGenerate social posts with Google Sheets and WordPress hands-free. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual captions is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nWeekly Schedule → Keep Valid Drafts → Frame the Assignment → Coordinator Agent → Unpack Sections → Persist Deliverable to Notion → Fingerprint for Idempotency → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to content generation without manual effort\n- Anyone automating captions in content creation\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Removes copy-paste errors\n- Standardizes the process every time\n- Saves hours of manual work each week\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; Google OAuth2 / service account; Notion integration token; OpenAI API key; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"1414e56f-6c39-50fd-3fa2-5d1b3b9519a3","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Failures are also parked in a dead-letter queue for replay. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-20],"id":"47db20aa-282a-5638-4ed6-7f0c97ac16ca","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🤖 AI cluster\n\nPurple nodes form one AI unit: the root node orchestrates, sub-nodes plug in via typed ports (model / memory / tools / parser). Swap the chat model without rewiring anything else. Costs scale with tokens — keep prompts lean and cap iterations.","width":360,"height":260,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-20],"id":"363da321-3cb4-d7cc-54f6-d72afbf582a1","name":"🤖 AI cluster"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🧹 Data quality\n\nDedupe/diff steps make re-runs safe: the same input twice will not create duplicate records. If you change the key fields, clear n8n's dedupe memory (node → 'Clear stored keys') before the next run.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-20],"id":"96e4ab20-4346-e9e0-394d-5938998e1f3c","name":"🧹 Data quality"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your captions process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1030,-20],"id":"3575d365-ccda-2d07-d504-470ac821da01","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Weekly Schedule":{"main":[[{"node":"Keep Valid Drafts","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Keep Valid Drafts":{"main":[[{"node":"Frame the Assignment","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Frame the Assignment":{"main":[[{"node":"Coordinator Agent","type":"main","index":0}]]},"OpenAI Chat Model":{"ai_languageModel":[[{"node":"Coordinator Agent","type":"ai_languageModel","index":0}]]},"Research Specialist (Sub-workflow)":{"ai_tool":[[{"node":"Coordinator Agent","type":"ai_tool","index":0}]]},"Draft Specialist (Sub-workflow)":{"ai_tool":[[{"node":"Coordinator Agent","type":"ai_tool","index":0}]]},"Enforce Result Schema":{"ai_outputParser":[[{"node":"Coordinator Agent","type":"ai_outputParser","index":0}]]},"Coordinator Agent":{"main":[[{"node":"Unpack Sections","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Unpack Sections":{"main":[[{"node":"Persist Deliverable to Notion","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Persist Deliverable to Notion":{"main":[[{"node":"Fingerprint for Idempotency","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fingerprint for Idempotency":{"main":[[{"node":"Drop Already-Processed Items","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Drop Already-Processed Items":{"main":[[{"node":"Serialize Run Output (CSV)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Serialize Run Output (CSV)":{"main":[[{"node":"Archive Row Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Archive Row Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow":{"main":[[{"node":"Record Sub-workflow Result","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Record Sub-workflow Result":{"main":[[{"node":"Enrich with Reference Data","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Enrich with Reference Data":{"main":[[{"node":"Fold In Enrichment Fields","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fold In Enrichment Fields":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Completion Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Completion Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Persist Run Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Persist Run Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Load Previous Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Load Previous Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Compute Drift vs Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Compute Drift vs Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Cap Batch Volume","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Cap Batch Volume":{"main":[[{"node":"Sort Drafts Newest First","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Sort Drafts Newest First":{"main":[[{"node":"Tag Pipeline Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Tag Pipeline Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Escalate Failure to Slack":{"main":[[{"node":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"96f63ede-58ee-4fd5-9e56-595aa2dab2b4","id":"FDX05606"}